Line3.EDC7C: We followed the blood and limbs back here. I can hear the screams of the unlucky ones still alive. I can’t leave them...but I doubt I’ll make it out of these woods. -Talmu
Line1.EDC7C: Please turn back. We have tracked the undead to these woods. They attacked our camp a few nights ago. I awoke to the cries of other loggers being dragged away into the night.
